2026-04-30 RAG upload support for txt md csv

Files changed:
- backend/document_loader.py
- backend/api.py
- frontend/index.html
- frontend/script.js

Summary:
- Added .txt support through TextLoader with autodetect_encoding enabled.
- Added .md support through TextLoader with autodetect_encoding enabled.
- Added .csv support through CSVLoader with autodetect_encoding enabled.
- Unified loader selection in DocumentLoader via _resolve_doc_type_and_loader().
- Added _resolve_page_number() so plain text and markdown default to page 1, and CSV rows map to stable row-based page numbers.
- Extended backend upload allowlist to accept .txt .md .csv.
- Extended frontend file input accept list to include .txt .md .csv.
- Added file icons for Text, Markdown, and CSV in the document list UI.

Verification:
- python -m py_compile backend/document_loader.py backend/api.py
- Smoke-tested loader output with sample.txt sample.md sample.csv
- Smoke test result:
  sample.txt 3 ['Text'] [1]
  sample.md 3 ['Markdown'] [1]
  sample.csv 6 ['CSV'] [1, 2]
